title: Accelerate your Development with FsHttp and FSharp.Data
description: Ditch cURL and Postman for readable HTTP queries and a parser that understands your data before you write a line of code
contentPreview: So you have to hit a new JSON API. Is there an SDK library? Nope. Forgot what flag you need for cURL? Time to use Postman. Postman asking you to sign in? Hmm... maybe you want a notebook experience? `pip install requests` but your Python installation is broken again...
